             was indicted for <rs id="t18210912-181-off1059" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210912-181-off1059" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210912-181-off1059" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210912-181-cd1060" type="crimeDate">14th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-181-off1059 t18210912-181-cd1060"></join>, one candlestick, value 2 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210912-181-victim1831" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Hitchcock
                  <interp inst="t18210912-181-victim1831" type="surname" value="Hitchcock"></interp>
